reviews.review_text: Omg I never never go to Burger King, I just was vanished also heard they served a great pouting. That said place my order got it quite fast and fresh. No problem at the counter it was quiet. However within the following half hour 3 girls showed up and started to berate the young lady seving and demanded keys to the washroom    then the 3 young girls stated to harass clients  but seemed to be afraid in pestering the likes of me. It lasted over 45 minutes and only once another employee made her entrance back to the store did it escalate to a point the police was to be called within the next 5 to 8 minutes of sarcasm and fowl language they left. Sadly theses young ladies had nothing better to do then to harass the hard-working young girl who had remained  polite quiet and silent despite the repeated attempts to make her feel like a piece of s@$$%t . Knowing well enough the wages the staff earn doesnt equate the verbal abuse she had to endure. So please be patient be kind be safe  and I assure you that whenever I stop by that place I will ensure that I stopped by eat a bite Knowing that who served me, his truly an amazing person who deserves all of my gratitude for a job well done. BTW: the pouting is affordable and awesome. Burgers  as good as any fast food
i like  atmosphere here and restaurant is very clean .last but not least service of employee was  very nice they are very friendly Thank you Food

The onion rings and the FF today were perfect!! Also the whoppers. I must mention that thank goodness the washrooms are not available anymore! Therefore there are not people coming in and out like a public restroom, homeless that stink are no longer here and the place feels fresh and clean... Whoever decided to shut down the washrooms deserve a standing ovation, thank you! I am definitely coming back more often!

I went there today near about 6:30pm .i think the guy working at front was new .he seems confused but the girl working at back was so good at her job. Store was busy  she was doing all the back work and also giving instructions to the guy. I had to wait for few minutes for my order but the food was amazing .keep up the good work

Such a low rating. Why? Its a fastfood joint with fast service. Jan 16th 11am my family went in and got great service. She was working alone and still knew what she was doin. Please give this lady a metal. Thank you.

Let me say that Burger King have the best burgers on the market. Well A&W come a close second. But back to Burger King burgers,  it had fresh tomatoes, fresh lettuce,  100% beef, it was The Ultimate Burger it was cooked to just perfect where the meat was still juicy but not pink. You would have to be a fool not too crowded this Burger Kings Burgers.

reviews.review_text: Great, open 24 hours!

Nice and friendly staff  , Good location , Burger King is so popular All over Canada, so Ill keep it short and get to the bottom line: Always fresh meat and ingredients, One of my number one places for french fries   seriously they serve you a big portion of fries I always say yes to Burger King Good luck

We stopped in for lunch there yesterday (03/20/19. Upon  ordering,I found out that their interactions wasnt working,So I had to go looking for an ATM,before we  could order,which was a little bit inconvenient. The Staff had to be asked twice to wipe down the table. The service  was a little slow,but the food was good considering that it was fast food.
